897
01:19:39,546 --> 01:19:41,446
Blefiraš! Blefiraš!

898
01:19:41,646 --> 01:19:43,646
Šifu te nije naučio tome!

899
01:19:43,846 --> 01:19:46,247
Ne. Sam sam shvatio.

