01:19:46,947 --> 01:19:48,147
Skaduš!

901
01:20:08,151 --> 01:20:09,325
Pogledajte!

902
01:20:10,451 --> 01:20:12,611
Zmajev Ratnik!

903
01:20:30,165 --> 01:20:31,305
Po!

904
01:20:39,556 --> 01:20:43,194
To je moj sin! Veliki,
ljupki kung-fu ratnik...

905
01:20:43,194 --> 01:20:44,563
je moj sin!

906
01:20:46,558 --> 01:20:48,048
Da!

907
01:20:49,658 --> 01:20:50,856
Hvala, tata.

908
01:21:00,585 --> 01:21:01,685
Zdravo, društvo.

909
01:21:06,461 --> 01:21:08,727
- Učitelju!
- Učitelju!

910
01:21:12,282 --> 01:21:15,008
Učitelju? Učitelj Šifu!

911
01:21:29,165 --> 01:21:30,465
Učitelju!

912
01:21:30,565 --> 01:21:32,666
Šifu! Šifu, jeste li dobro?

913
01:21:34,366 --> 01:21:36,767
Po, živ si.

914
01:21:37,567 --> 01:21:39,467
Ili smo obojica mrtvi.

915
01:21:39,567 --> 01:21:41,367
Ne, učitelju, nisam poginuo.

916
01:21:41,467 --> 01:21:43,368
Porazio sam Tai Lunga.

917
01:21:43,368 --> 01:21:45,368
Jesi?

918
01:21:50,269 --> 01:21:53,270
I jeste kako je Ugvej predskazao.

919
01:21:54,570 --> 01:21:57,470
Ti jesi Zmajev Ratnik.

920
01:21:58,670 --> 01:22:00,471
Doneo si mir...

921
01:22:00,571 --> 01:22:02,571
ovoj Dolini.

922
01:22:03,971 --> 01:22:07,172
I... I meni.

923
01:22:07,672 --> 01:22:09,672
Hvala.

924
01:22:10,673 --> 01:22:13,373
Hvala, Po.

925
01:22:14,373 --> 01:22:16,774
Hvala. Hvala.

926
01:22:22,375 --> 01:22:24,775
Ne! Učitelju!

927
01:22:25,075 --> 01:22:27,276
Ne, ne, ne! Nemojte
umreti, Šifu, molim Vas!

928
01:22:27,476 --> 01:22:29,576
Ne umirem, idiote jedan!

929
01:22:29,976 --> 01:22:32,076
Ah, Zmajev Ratniče.

930
01:22:33,577 --> 01:22:36,677
Jednostavno sam našao svoj mir.

931
01:22:37,077 --> 01:22:39,078
Konačno.

932
01:22:41,178 --> 01:22:43,578
Treba da prestanem da pričam?

933
